<td rowspan="4" style="vertical-align:top; padding-left:1em; padding-right:1em; text-align:justify; width:92%;">
<p><b>Muisca abdigalda</b> tiyir soka lospasa va <a href="/wiki/Muisca_sane" title="Muisca sane">Muisca</a> saneikeem koe istefo tawavo ke refe <a href="/wiki/Kolombia" title="Kolombia">Kolombia</a> sokasane abdi espanafa olgalicura. Balemoyi abdigaldaki tiyid : MuyquytÃ¡ Zipazgo cosxo is Hunza Zacazgo cosxo is Iraca tumtaxo is Tundama tumtaxo voxis konako mivvexaxo.
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Xanta">Xanta</h2></div>
<p>Mali lekeugal, Muisca va yerumara wali staba ksubeyed numen sina kadayad vangluyara ke yona doda. Ison vuwafa waldura gu vindara wal amidafa doda iku banafa fiste zo divatceyer, isen dofa vegedusa lagara dum lavakiraf bolk ta midura va ontinafa taya, isen sayakafa tanara ta likera va volnafa mikra dum Panche is Muzo, va lomantafa vangluyara tuadrayar. Bata kotcoba di tiyir tazukafa riga ke abdigalda.
</p><p>Lopof andik ta ardil is targuca is gaderopafi is skapafi roti va sint likeyed ise va sintafa doda lalevbenpluyud. Bata koboda va geja daskiyid. Voxen cenen okilik va gadera va staba is doda me mbi deswayad nume grustara ke dodeem is stabeem zo nendoyeyed. Opelon cenesik va intafa ardilafa tirka laumasiyir numaze va vamoefa gorara ronovaskiyir ise va kiewega loote mbi kserayar.
</p><p>Zipazgo cosxo moni 1450 awiyir, gadenon gan Saguamachica gejayasa va Panche mikra, aze kali 1541 lapteyer viele espanafa olgalicura va istexo ke refa Kolombia ceneson tenukeyer.
</p>
<figure class="mw-halign-left" typeof="mw:File/Thumb"><a href="/wiki/Iyeltak:Museo_del_oro,_Bogot%C3%A1_man_whose_eyes_and_mouth_have_been_made_from_double_strips.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Museo_del_oro%2C_Bogot%C3%A1_man_whose_eyes_and_mouth_have_been_made_from_double_strips.jpg/250px-Museo_del_oro%2C_Bogot%C3%A1_man_whose_eyes_and_mouth_have_been_made_from_double_strips.jpg" decoding="async" width="250" height="375" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Museo_del_oro%2C_Bogot%C3%A1_man_whose_eyes_and_mouth_have_been_made_from_double_strips.jpg/330px-Museo_del_oro%2C_Bogot%C3%A1_man_whose_eyes_and_mouth_have_been_made_from_double_strips.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1037" data-file-height="1555"></a><figcaption><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #5e5f62; font-size: 95%;">Muisca balumaks va lan mepilkomodan <i>Zipa</i> nafalik, re viden dene Tcila ke Moava koe BogotÃ¡.</span></div></figcaption></figure>
<p>Cosxo ke Muisca abdigalda va kipi ke ontinafa gola ke Ronefa Rodega koe Kolombia modivatceyer, koe refa <a href="/wiki/KolombiaCundinamarcaWinka" title="KolombiaCundinamarcaWinka">Cundinamarca</a> winka isu <a href="/wiki/KolombiaBoyac%C3%A1Winka" title="KolombiaBoyacÃ¡Winka">BoyacÃ¡</a> isu <a href="/wiki/KolombiaSantanderWinka" title="KolombiaSantanderWinka">Santander</a>. Koe Cundinamarca, xopo tiyid azekexa ke <a href="/w/index.php?title=Bogot%C3%A1&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="BogotÃ¡ (me tisu bu)">BogotÃ¡</a> is <a href="/wiki/Ubat%C3%A9" title="UbatÃ©">UbatÃ©</a> is Pacho krant isu <a href="/wiki/Fusagasug%C3%A1" title="FusagasugÃ¡">FusagasugÃ¡</a> isu <a href="/wiki/Tenza" title="Tenza">Tenza</a> isu <a href="/wiki/C%C3%A1queza" title="CÃ¡queza">CÃ¡queza</a> ; koe BoyacÃ¡ : <a href="/wiki/Tunja" title="Tunja">Tunja</a> is <a href="/wiki/Moniquir%C3%A1" title="MoniquirÃ¡">MoniquirÃ¡</a> is <a href="/wiki/Chiquinquir%C3%A1" title="ChiquinquirÃ¡">ChiquinquirÃ¡</a> is <a href="/wiki/Duitama" title="Duitama">Duitama</a> is <a href="/wiki/Villa_de_Leyva" title="Villa de Leyva">Villa de Leyva</a> is <a href="/wiki/Sogamoso" title="Sogamoso">Sogamoso</a> ; vagee Santander : wale <a href="/w/index.php?title=Su%C3%A1rez_(kuksa)&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="SuÃ¡rez (kuksa) (me tisu bu)">SuÃ¡rez</a> kuksa isu <a href="/wiki/Chicamocha_(kuksa)" title="Chicamocha (kuksa)">Chicamocha</a>.
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Grustara">Grustara</h2></div>
<p>Muisca abdigalda vas cosxo vas mon 47 000 kmÂ² ruldayar, valentu Chicamocha gola vage PÃ¡ramo de Sumapaz gee BogotÃ¡, is vataltu <a href="/wiki/V%C3%A9lez_(Santander)" title="VÃ©lez (Santander)">VÃ©lez</a> is <a href="/wiki/Zipac%C3%B3n" title="ZipacÃ³n">ZipacÃ³n</a> varon datca ke Ronefa Rodega tite azeka ke Meta golapa. Sanelia ke cosxo tiyir vas mon 1200000 irubasik ba artlakira ke espanik.
</p>

    Muisca abdigalda tiyir soka lospasa va Muisca saneikeem koe istefo tawavo ke refe Kolombia sokasane abdi espanafa olgalicura. Balemoyi abdigaldaki tiyidÂ : MuyquytÃ¡ Zipazgo cosxo is Hunza Zacazgo cosxo is Iraca tumtaxo is Tundama tumtaxo voxis konako mivvexaxo.

    Xanta

    Mali lekeugal, Muisca va yerumara wali staba ksubeyed numen sina kadayad vangluyara ke yona doda. Ison vuwafa waldura gu vindara wal amidafa doda iku banafa fiste zo divatceyer, isen dofa vegedusa lagara dum lavakiraf bolk ta midura va ontinafa taya, isen sayakafa tanara ta likera va volnafa mikra dum Panche is Muzo, va lomantafa vangluyara tuadrayar. Bata kotcoba di tiyir tazukafa riga ke abdigalda.

    Lopof andik ta ardil is targuca is gaderopafi is skapafi roti va sint likeyed ise va sintafa doda lalevbenpluyud. Bata koboda va geja daskiyid. Voxen cenen okilik va gadera va staba is doda me mbi deswayad nume grustara ke dodeem is stabeem zo nendoyeyed. Opelon cenesik va intafa ardilafa tirka laumasiyir numaze va vamoefa gorara ronovaskiyir ise va kiewega loote mbi kserayar.

    Zipazgo cosxo moni 1450 awiyir, gadenon gan Saguamachica gejayasa va Panche mikra, aze kali 1541 lapteyer viele espanafa olgalicura va istexo ke refa Kolombia ceneson tenukeyer.

## Xanta
Mali lekeugal, Muisca va yerumara wali staba ksubeyed numen sina kadayad vangluyara ke yona doda. Ison vuwafa waldura gu vindara wal amidafa doda iku banafa fiste zo divatceyer, isen dofa vegedusa lagara dum lavakiraf bolk ta midura va ontinafa taya, isen sayakafa tanara ta likera va volnafa mikra dum Panche is Muzo, va lomantafa vangluyara tuadrayar. Bata kotcoba di tiyir tazukafa riga ke abdigalda.  Lopof andik ta ardil is targuca is gaderopafi is skapafi roti va sint likeyed ise va sintafa doda lalevbenpluyud. Bata koboda va geja daskiyid. Voxen cenen okilik va gadera va staba is doda me mbi deswayad nume grustara ke dodeem is stabeem zo nendoyeyed. Opelon cenesik va intafa ardilafa tirka laumasiyir numaze va vamoefa gorara ronovaskiyir ise va kiewega loote mbi kserayar.  Zipazgo cosxo moni 1450 awiyir, gadenon gan Saguamachica gejayasa va Panche mikra, aze kali 1541 lapteyer viele espanafa olgalicura va istexo ke refa Kolombia ceneson tenukeyer.  [![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Museo_del_oro%2C_Bogot%C3%A1_man_whose_eyes_and_mouth_have_been_made_from_double_strips.jpg/250px-Museo_del_oro%2C_Bogot%C3%A1_man_whose_eyes_and_mouth_have_been_made_from_double_strips.jpg)](https://avk.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iyeltak:Museo_del_oro,_Bogot%C3%A1_man_whose_eyes_and_mouth_have_been_made_from_double_strips.jpg)Muisca balumaks va lan mepilkomodan _Zipa_ nafalik, re viden dene Tcila ke Moava koe BogotÃ¡. Cosxo ke Muisca abdigalda va kipi ke ontinafa gola ke Ronefa Rodega koe Kolombia modivatceyer, koe refa [Cundinamarca](https://avk.wikipedia.org/wiki/KolombiaCundinamarcaWinka "KolombiaCundinamarcaWinka") winka isu [BoyacÃ¡](https://avk.wikipedia.org/wiki/KolombiaBoyac%C3%A1Winka "KolombiaBoyacÃ¡Winka") isu [Santander](https://avk.wikipedia.org/wiki/KolombiaSantanderWinka "KolombiaSantanderWinka"). ## Xanta
Mali lekeugal, Muisca va yerumara wali staba ksubeyed numen sina kadayad vangluyara ke yona doda. Ison vuwafa waldura gu vindara wal amidafa doda iku banafa fiste zo divatceyer, isen dofa vegedusa lagara dum lavakiraf bolk ta midura va ontinafa taya, isen sayakafa tanara ta likera va volnafa mikra dum Panche is Muzo, va lomantafa vangluyara tuadrayar. Bata kotcoba di tiyir tazukafa riga ke abdigalda.  Lopof andik ta ardil is targuca is gaderopafi is skapafi roti va sint likeyed ise va sintafa doda lalevbenpluyud. Bata koboda va geja daskiyid. Voxen cenen okilik va gadera va staba is doda me mbi deswayad nume grustara ke dodeem is stabeem zo nendoyeyed. Opelon cenesik va intafa ardilafa tirka laumasiyir numaze va vamoefa gorara ronovaskiyir ise va kiewega loote mbi kserayar.
